Class InitializeMojo

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextEnabled, Mojo

    @Mojo(name="initialize",
      defaultPhase=INITIALIZE)
public class InitializeMojo
extends AbstractBWMojo

    This goal will initialize additional properties to use in next goals. It is the first goal called by the bw-ear lifecycle in the initialize phase.

    Author:
    Radwane Mabchour

      • execute

        public void execute()
             throws MojoExecutionException
        Description copied from class: AbstractBWMojo

        The execute method of this Mojo will :

        • check that the BusinessWorks project exists
        • copy the Designer5.prefs file
        • copy the .designtimelibs file useful for setting a TIBCO environment for the project being built.
